::KitKat::

She woke up from her nap and walked out of her quarters.  She saw 
Quickstrike standing by the entrance of the cave.  She was in beast mode and 
walked over to him.
"Don't look so happy to be here."  She smirked at him.  She transformed into 
bot mode and drew her gun.
"Hey target practice."
She picked up a rock, threw it into the air as high as she could and shot 
it.
"Your turn."
